<plot>In the tiny European country of Arvania, the king is a young boy who is enthralled with the magazine adventures of American cowboy Bill Stevens. When Stevens and his Wild West Show pay a visit to Arvania, the king is delighted. But the wily Regent plots to kidnap the king and take his place as ruler. But he has not reckoned on the king's new cowboy pal.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?587930</url></doc>
